## 🚫 PART 6: Pitfalls to Avoid

| Mistake | Why It Kills Your Score | Prevention |
|---------|----------------------|------------|
| Trying to build everything | Half-finished product | Pick 4 core features, polish to perfection |
| Live API failures during demo | Judges don't give second chances | Pre-cache responses, have fallbacks |
| Generic ChatGPT wrapper | "So you just call an API?" | Emphasize decomposition + triangulation logic |
| Ugly UI | Signals "weekend project" | Invest 30% of time on UI polish |
| All talk, no demo | Loses instantly | 60% of pitch should be live demo |
| No business angle | "Cool tech, now what?" | EU AI Act compliance + SaaS pricing |

