## 📋 PART 7: Hackathon Timeline (24 hours)

| Hour | Task | Deliverable |
|------|------|-------------|
| 0-1 | Setup project, install deps, design system | Running Next.js + FastAPI skeleton |
| 1-3 | Build claim decomposition engine | Working decomposition with LLM |
| 3-5 | Build verification engine (Wikipedia + Wikidata + Fact Check API) | Claims verified against 3 sources |
| 5-7 | Build WebSocket streaming pipeline | Real-time updates flowing to frontend |
| 7-10 | Build main dashboard UI (split panel, heatmap, trust score) | Core UI complete |
| 10-12 | Build detailed report view + source evidence cards | Drill-down verification details |
| 12-14 | Build trust certificate export | Downloadable PDF report |
| 14-16 | Domain mode selector + polish verification logic | Multi-domain support |
| 16-18 | UI polish: animations, transitions, loading states, dark mode | Premium feel |
| 18-20 | End-to-end testing, bug fixes, demo data preparation | Stable demo |
| 20-22 | Prepare pitch, rehearse demo, record backup video | Pitch ready |
| 22-24 | Final polish | Ready to win |

